headline.print_headline: N.F.L. Suspends Its Study of the Effect of Concussions on Retired Players
headline.seo: N.F.L. Suspends Its Study of Concussions
headline.main: N.F.L. Suspends Its Study on Concussions

docs.lead_paragraph: The league’s study of long-term effects of head injuries on retired players was put on hold amid criticism of matters ranging from poor statistical sampling to conflicts of interest.
docs.snippet: The league’s study of long-term effects of head injuries on retired players was put on hold amid criticism of matters ranging from poor statistical sampling to conflicts of interest.

headline.print_headline: New Goal for the Obese: Zero Gain in Pregnancy
headline.seo: Study Sets Tough Diet Goals for Obese Pregnant Women
headline.main: New Goal for the Obese: Zero Gain in Pregnancy

docs.lead_paragraph: A study of weight gain by obese women in pregnancy will try to keep them from putting on any pounds.
docs.snippet: A study of weight gain by obese women in pregnancy will try to keep them from putting on any pounds.
